{"tid":2489910,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：習近平將以視象方式出席中法德領導人氣候變化峰會","createTime":"2021-04-15T08:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T09:10:14.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"43e07fc70f5053f85468d0d0ed5ed7838aba71b1","tid":2489910,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:35:25.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平將以視象方式，出席中法德領導人氣候變化峰會。<br />\n<br />\n另外，訪問上海的美國總統氣候問題特使克里，覲見中方官員。中國生態環境部表示，接見克里的是氣候變化事務特使解振華，而上海會談的目的，是推進在應對氣候變化方面的合作，並就聯合國氣候變化框架公約第26次締約方大會，彼此交換意見。<br />\n<br />\n美國駐北京大使館表示，在克里前往行程下一站的南韓首爾之前，沒有安排任何傳媒採訪活動。<br />\n<br />\n美國是全球最大碳排放國，美中兩國都設定了在未來幾十年，實現碳中和的目標，不過外界指控中國的目標不夠進取。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585954-20210415.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585954-20210415.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sJq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=6fe82100\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585954-20210415.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=16d20c25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585954-20210415.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"07b141c5b63a116123f2f44e18e00868218975d2","tid":2489910,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"又嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/788e1e50-4ab2-11eb-9131-005056a98db9/w:1280/p:16x9/Capture-270.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2F788e1e50-4ab2-11eb-9131-005056a98db9%2Fw%3A1280%2Fp%3A16x9%2FCapture-270.webp&h=e88c635b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://dw-media.tkww.hk/dams/dwproduct/image/202012/30/5fec9548e4b087a37b8d105d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdw-media.tkw